thread.title: Aletha Kochius-McNaught
thread.title_full: Mystery Tackle Box reviewed by Aletha Kochius-McNaught

author: Aletha Kochius-McNaught
title: Aletha Kochius-McNaught
text:
Mystery Tackle Box is the best monthly tackle subscription there is. It's always cool to see what new baits come each month and to be introduced to new products. Customer service is top notch. Shipping to Canada is free, what more could i ask for?!?
Another neat feature is the Catch Co. boxes that are offered. it's a great way to get a bunch of predetermined baits at a fraction of the price. I've grabbed a few of these boxes in the past and i managed to scoff an amazing deal on BioSpawn soft plastics on black friday for 40% off.
You won't be disappointed by MTB, and you are guaranteed a 90% increase in hook up ratio! ;)
